## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Start backend server (`npm start` in backend/) and verify `POST /api/studybuddy/chat` returns a valid response with a test PDF.

### Manual Verification
- Start both servers, navigate to `/study-buddy`.
- Upload a sample PDF, ask a question, verify the AI responds with content from the document.
- Test drag-and-drop upload, remove PDF, re-upload.
- Test suggested question chips.
- Verify responsive layout on different screen widths.
